        "info": "QR Code Link to This Post 🏡 Looking for a place that actually feels like home? Our spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartments have everything you need—and more! 💲 Pricing: • 3 Bedrooms starting at $975 per month ✨ Apartment Features: • Spacious floor plan with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms • Fully equipped kitchen with dishwasher • Private deck or patio • Tons of closet space • Controlled access for added security 🌿 Community Amenities: • Playground • Softball field • Tennis & basketball courts • On-site dog park 📍 Conveniently located close to shopping, restaurants, colleges, and plenty of recreational activities. 💡 Included Utilities: Water, sewer, and garbage are paid! 💲 Details: • Security Deposit: Equal to one month’s rent • Application Fee: $50 per adult • Pet-friendly buildings available 🎉 Current tenants can earn a referral bonus—ask us for details! We complete background checks, credit history reviews, landlord reference checks, and employment verification. ⏰ Office Hours: Monday–Friday: 8:00 AM – 7:00 PM Saturday: 10:00 AM – 3:00 PM Sunday: Closed 📞 Call us today: show contact info 📸 Photos are examples only. Babinski Properties — A Taste of the Country in the Heart of the City.",
