        "mainpic": "ebfab90d-db3d-4373-913f-dfe6f7b63606",
        "msg": "QR Code Link to This Post See more photos and SCHEDULE A SHOWING at: http://showinghotline.com/lc/de512df029 No, it's not a hyperlink. :-( You still have to copy-and-paste this link into the address bar on your web browser. Budget-friendly apartment with great amenities 138 N Sycamore Ave - 12, Sioux Falls, SD, 57110 $695 per month Available now 1 bed, 1 full bath Welcome to your dream apartment! This stunning rental property is perfect for anyone looking for a comfortable and convenient living experience. The apartment comes with a plethora of amenities to make your stay enjoyable and stress-free. Plus every apartment is entirely handicap accessible, including roll-in showers! This beautiful apartment includes all utilities in the monthly rent, so you don't have to worry about additional bills. It features a lounge with television and streaming services included, multiple gathering areas, laundry room, workout room, and a game room, ensuring that there's something for everyone. You'll also have access to a coffee and snack station stocked at no additional charge, a shared chefs kitchen with locked cabinets for private food storage, and a large gathering room that's perfect for hosting private events… all included! Additional unique amenities include, popcorn machine, vending machines and a business center with computers, printer and internet included. Other amenities include indoor lockable bike storage, a garden room, access to an outdoor garden, and guest suites available for rent. As well as indoor garbage service so you never have to step outside on cold days. And bus service is right around the corner to provide easy access to public transportation. You'll even have the option to opt-in to an optional meal plan if you're too busy to cook. Security is a top priority, so you can rest assured that you'll be safe and secure in this building. With secured entry and 24/7 security, you can have peace of mind at all times. Included with all lease agreements is our Resident Benefits Package. Because we bundle services for things tenants typically pay for out of pocket, we help our tenants simplify, lower expenses and keep utility bills to a minimum. Click the link to read more about the benefits of renting from Luke Properties: https://luke.properties/benefits ($49/mo) This apartment is perfect for anyone who wants to have everything they need at their fingertips without breaking the budget. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to make this beautiful apartment your new home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing! (rent increases of an estimated 3% occur automatically on January 1st of each year) Rooms and Interior . Recently rehabbed . Open floor plan . Carpet floors . Living room . Garden apartment . First floor walkup . Master bath Kitchen and Bath . Eat-in kitchen . Chefs kitchen . Hardwood cabinets . Refrigerator . Microwave Utilities and Extras . Central heat . Laundry on-site . Cable ready . Internet access available Building and Surroundings . Small building . Recently renovated . Secured entry . Wheelchair access . Patio . Garden . Yard . 90+ Walkscore . Park nearby Amenities and Services . Fitness center . Bike room . Business center . Media room / clubhouse . Full service . Private party room . Lounge / club room . Coffee service . Guest suite Lease Terms . No pets . Gas and electric included . One year lease . No smoking . No smoking building . Parking included . 2 parking spots . No dogs . No cats . Trash removal included . Water/sewer included . Snow removal included . Lawn care included Contact Us: Luke Properties, LLC Serena Thomas show contact info See more photos and SCHEDULE A SHOWING at: http://showinghotline.com/lc/de512df029",
