        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post See more photos and SCHEDULE A SHOWING at: http://schedule-a-viewing.com/lc/9a2a8ad04c No, it's not a hyperlink. :-( You still have to copy-and-paste this link into the address bar on your web browser. One bedroom apartment with garage near downtown Sioux Falls 405 S Sycamore Ave & Garage 4 - 104, Sioux Falls, SD, 57110 $775 per month Available now 1 bed, 1 full bath 600 sq. ft. Welcome to Sycamore Village, a beautifully renovated apartment complex located in the heart of Sioux Falls, SD, now under professional management! These apartments in East Sioux Falls are freshly remodeled and ready to welcome new residents. This one-bedroom, one-bathroom apartment offers a blend of comfort and style. The recently updated kitchen features hardwood cabinets and modern appliances, including a dishwasher, refrigerator, and stove/oven. The dining room and living room boast hardwood floors, while the bedrooms are carpeted for your comfort. The open floor plans offer plenty of space to relax or entertain. The large closets and shelving will give you plenty of storage space, too! There is on-site laundry! The apartment also comes with garage parking, which is perfect for winter and to store extra items. The building offers secured entry for your peace of mind. Garage parking is included with additional off-street parking lot. The building is a no-smoking and no-pets environment, ensuring a clean and fresh living space for all residents. Come and experience the comfort and convenience of living at Sycamore Village. The excellent location, near 10th & Sycamore, is close to some of the best shopping and entertainment that Sioux Falls has to offer. Included with all lease agreements is our Resident Benefits Package. Because we bundle services for things tenants typically pay for out of pocket, we help our tenants simplify, lower expenses and keep utility bills to a minimum. Click the link to read more about the benefits of renting from 