perties/benefits ($49/mo) This is a quiet neighborhood, and we are looking for a quiet tenant to call this home. You've just found your next Sioux Falls home!​ (rent increases of just 2% occur automatically on January 1st of each year) Rooms and Interior . Recently rehabbed . Hardwood floors . Carpet floors . Living room Kitchen and Bath . Hardwood floors . Stove/oven . Kitchen recently updated . Eat-in kitchen . Hardwood cabinets . Dishwasher . Refrigerator Utilities and Extras . Central heat . Off-street parking . Laundry on-site . Cable ready . Wired internet available Building and Surroundings . Recently renovated . Secured entry . Sprinkler system . 90+ Walkscore . Park nearby Lease Terms . No pets . Tenant pays all utilities . One year lease . No smoking . No smoking building . Parking included . No dogs . No cats . Snow removal included . Lawn care included Contact Us: Luke Properties, LLC Serena Thomas show contact info See more photos and SCHEDULE A SHOWING at: http://showinghotline.com/lc/99c5d6b04c",
