        "description": "QR Code Link to This Post See more photos and SCHEDULE A SHOWING at: http://schedule-a-viewing.com/lc/ca9fdc004b No, it's not a hyperlink. :-( You still have to copy-and-paste this link into the address bar on your web browser. Beautiful three bedroom twin home with open floor plan 9657 W Tunis Dr, Sioux Falls, SD, 57106 $2195 per month Available now 3 beds, 3 full baths 1777 sq. ft. Enjoy the comfort and convenience of this newer 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath ranch-style twin home offering 1,777 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space. Built in 2024, this home features an open-concept floor plan with modern finishes and plenty of room to spread out. The spacious kitchen is equipped with a large center island, pantry, and all major appliances—including a refrigerator, electric range, microwave, dishwasher, and disposal—making it ideal for both everyday living and entertaining. The bright and inviting living room opens to a private deck, creating the perfect space to relax or enjoy the outdoors. The main level includes a private primary suite with double closets and an attached ¾ bath, along with the convenience of main-floor laundry. Downstairs, the fully finished walkout basement offers a large family room with a cozy electric fireplace, two additional bedrooms, and extra living space that provides flexibility for guests, a home office, or recreation. Additional features include central air conditioning, natural gas heat, an attached two-stall garage, and low-maintenance twin home living. Located in a desirable Sioux Falls neighborhood with easy access to shopping, dining, schools, and parks, this modern home offers all the amenities you need. Contact us today to schedule a showing! Included with all lease agreements is our Resident Benefits Package. Because we bundle services for things tenants typically pay for out of pocket, we help our tenants simplify, lower expenses and keep utility bills to a minimum. Click the link to read more about the benefits of renting from Luke Properties: https://luke.properties/benefits ($49/mo) This is a quiet area and we are looking for a quiet tenant to call this home. You've just found your next Sioux Falls home!​ (rent increases of an estimated 3% occur automatically on January 1st of each year) Lease Terms . No dogs . No cats Contact Us: Luke Properties, LLC Serena Thomas show contact info See more photos and SCHEDULE A SHOWING at: http://schedule-a-viewing.com/lc/ca9fdc004b",
