efits of renting from Luke Properties: https://luke.properties/benefits ($49/mo) This is a quiet area and we are looking for a quiet tenant to call this home. You've just found your next Sioux Falls home!​ (rent increases of an estimated 3% occur automatically on January 1st of each year) Lease Terms . No dogs . No cats Contact Us: Luke Properties, LLC Serena Thomas show contact info See more photos and SCHEDULE A SHOWING at: http://schedule-a-viewing.com/lc/ca9fdc004b",
